store.name: store
store.short_desc: Get a cache store instance by name, wrapped in a repository.

repository.name: repository
repository.short_desc: Create a new cache repository with the given implementation.

getDefaultDriver.name: getDefaultDriver
getDefaultDriver.short_desc: Get the default cache driver name.

setDefaultDriver.name: setDefaultDriver
setDefaultDriver.short_desc: Set the default cache driver name.

extend.name: extend
extend.short_desc: Register a custom driver creator Closure.

has.name: has
has.short_desc: Determine if an item exists in the cache.

missing.name: missing
missing.short_desc: Determine if an item doesn't exist in the cache.

get.name: get
get.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache by key.

many.name: many
many.short_desc: Retrieve multiple items from the cache by key.
many.long_desc: Items not found in the cache will have a null value.

getMultiple.name: getMultiple
getMultiple.short_desc: Obtains multiple cache items by their unique keys.
getMultiple.hint_desc: A list of key => value pairs. Cache keys that do not exist or are stale will have $default as value.
exceptions:
MUST be thrown if $keys is neither an array nor a Traversable,
  or if any of the $keys are not a legal value.

keys.name: keys
keys.short_desc: A list of keys that can obtained in a single operation.

default.name: default
default.short_desc: Default value to return for keys that do not exist.

pull.name: pull
pull.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache and delete it.

put.name: put
put.short_desc: Store an item in the cache.

set.name: set
set.short_desc: Persists data in the cache, uniquely referenced by a key with an optional expiration TTL time.
set.hint_desc: True on success and false on failure.
exceptions: MUST be thrown if the $key string is not a legal value.

key.name: key
key.short_desc: The key of the item to store.

value.name: value
value.short_desc: The value of the item to store, must be serializable.

ttl.name: ttl
ttl.short_desc:
Optional. The TTL value of this item. If no value is sent and
                                     the driver supports TTL then the library may set a default value
                                     for it or let the driver take care of that.

putMany.name: putMany
putMany.short_desc: Store multiple items in the cache for a given number of seconds.

setMultiple.name: setMultiple
setMultiple.short_desc: Persists a set of key => value pairs in the cache, with an optional TTL.
setMultiple.hint_desc: True on success and false on failure.
exceptions:
MUST be thrown if $values is neither an array nor a Traversable,
  or if any of the $values are not a legal value.

values.name: values
values.short_desc: A list of key => value pairs for a multiple-set operation.

ttl.name: ttl
ttl.short_desc:
Optional. The TTL value of this item. If no value is sent and
                                      the driver supports TTL then the library may set a default value
                                      for it or let the driver take care of that.

add.name: add
add.short_desc: Store an item in the cache if the key does not exist.

increment.name: increment
increment.short_desc: Increment the value of an item in the cache.

decrement.name: decrement
decrement.short_desc: Decrement the value of an item in the cache.

forever.name: forever
forever.short_desc: Store an item in the cache indefinitely.

remember.name: remember
remember.short_desc: Get an item from the cache, or execute the given Closure and store the result.

sear.name: sear
sear.short_desc: Get an item from the cache, or execute the given Closure and store the result forever.

rememberForever.name: rememberForever
rememberForever.short_desc: Get an item from the cache, or execute the given Closure and store the result forever.

forget.name: forget
forget.short_desc: Remove an item from the cache.

delete.name: delete
delete.short_desc: Delete an item from the cache by its unique key.
delete.hint_desc: True if the item was successfully removed. False if there was an error.
exceptions: MUST be thrown if the $key string is not a legal value.

key.name: key
key.short_desc: The unique cache key of the item to delete.

deleteMultiple.name: deleteMultiple
deleteMultiple.short_desc: Deletes multiple cache items in a single operation.
deleteMultiple.hint_desc: True if the items were successfully removed. False if there was an error.
exceptions:
MUST be thrown if $keys is neither an array nor a Traversable,
  or if any of the $keys are not a legal value.

keys.name: keys
keys.short_desc: A list of string-based keys to be deleted.

clear.name: clear
clear.short_desc: Wipes clean the entire cache's keys.
clear.hint_desc: True on success and false on failure.

tags.name: tags
tags.short_desc: Begin executing a new tags operation if the store supports it.

setDefaultCacheTime.name: setDefaultCacheTime
setDefaultCacheTime.short_desc: Set the default cache time in seconds.

offsetExists.name: offsetExists
offsetExists.short_desc: Determine if a cached value exists.

offsetGet.name: offsetGet
offsetGet.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache by key.

offsetSet.name: offsetSet
offsetSet.short_desc: Store an item in the cache for the default time.

offsetUnset.name: offsetUnset
offsetUnset.short_desc: Remove an item from the cache.

mixin.name: mixin
mixin.short_desc: Mix another object into the class.

macroCall.name: macroCall
macroCall.short_desc: Dynamically handle calls to the class.

flush.name: flush
flush.short_desc: Remove all items from the cache.

getDirectory.name: getDirectory
getDirectory.short_desc: Get the working directory of the cache.
